Script writing (or screenwriting) is the process of writing stories in the 
screenplay medium. Script writing is writing down the movement, actions, expression 
and dialogue of the characters in screenplay, in screenplay format.



// ES6 syntax
function Person(){
  this.age = 0;

  setInterval(() => {
    // `this` now refers to the Person object, brilliant!
    this.age++;
  }, 1000);
}

var p = new Person();
